{
  "stem": "3988.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And for that, you know, I used to get an extra bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, I used to hold that big kettle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, they had to dig, you know, the soup, and put in the soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I used to hold the kettle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And sometimes I bent back a little bit, the kettle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "See, this way, there was more soup left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, because whatever was left in the kettle, you know, we used to share it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then I took that bowl of soup and trade it with somebody else for a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because the other guy-- the soup would fill them up more than the piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So they gave me a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that piece of bread-- I had an extra piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I could take it to work, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had-- which nobody had a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to put the piece of bread in my uniform, sleep in it, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't-- because the same thing-- I had no place where to put it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, so I used to-- and I had a piece of extra bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you know, I had a little bit of extra food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that came because account of the kapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then one time, he gave me, you know, to-- because, you know, we worked with Polish people in the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He used to gave me to smuggle into the camp a package of tobacco, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if they catch you to, you know, smuggle in, they hang you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- but I mean, if I-- you know, when you get an extra bowl of soup, you know, why not?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
